  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, we would-- something we would never, never, never dream of doing, otherwise, in order to make sure that we could get leave there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that point it was critical.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother and I burned those books in our own furnace in the house, and it still hurts me when I think of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was necessary at that time, because these secret police people were there all day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they left in the evening, they sealed the rooms that-- that we were working in, packing in, and we only had the bedrooms and bathrooms to use.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It does.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the gestapo, these people were pretty ignorant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were undereducated or uneducated, and they wouldn't know the difference, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was partly what had happened, because I say that in my-- when I describe my best friend and how she left me, or how she wouldn't talk to me anymore in the story-- which I have not yet published.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have published most of the others-- that I feel at the end there, and I said that I felt-- that I-- it seemed, when I was alone-- going home alone at that time in the street car after our meeting in the woods, 'it seemed an era of my adolescent life had come to an end, and I would have to grow up much faster than I had planned to face the reality of a new and different Germany.' And I locked myself in my room after that because I felt helpless and frustrated.",
      "word_count": 95
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I realized that I would not be able to go the normal course of schooling that I had planned, and going to the university afterwards.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
